# .forceignore — controls what SFDX ignores during push/pull

# Managed package metadata
**/wave/**
**/featureParameters/**

# Experience Cloud compiled assets (regenerated on deploy)
**/experiences/**/config/**
**/digitalExperiences/**/.sfdx/**

# Standard objects we don't want to overwrite in target org
**/objects/Activity/**
**/objects/CaseHistory/**
**/objects/ContactHistory/**
**/objects/AccountHistory/**
**/objects/OpportunityHistory/**

# Test data files (loaded separately via SFDX data commands)
**/data/**

# Project docs — not deployable metadata
**/projectDocs/**
